s vorliegende methodenorientierte Lehrbuch vollständig die Keynesianische und Neukeynesianische Theorie geschlossener und offener Volkswirtschaften ab.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 15. Jun 2019) 70(DE-601)1062389650(DE-588)4037174-8aMakroökonomie2gnd 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Economics / Theory.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG OWV ebook Paket Lehrbücher Wirtschaftswiss. 2016z9783110491104oZDB-23-OLW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2016z9783110485158oZDB-23-DBV0 cEPUBz97831104645280 cprintz978311046417740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110464191423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110464191.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA14ALL  aPDA15STM  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2HUM  aPDA3STM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DBVb2016  aZDB-23-DGGb2016  aZDB-23-OLWb2016